{"tid":982931,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"無啦 利穎怡入左紙就嫁人","createTime":"2019-01-15T13:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T09:52:12.000Z","uid":38456,"like":11,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfc891745a333bd87dc562606393d0a776ebc84","tid":982931,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190115/photo/bkn-20190115205839957-0115_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190115213243\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190115205839957-0115_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190115213243&h=e6c2f544&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190115/photo/bkn-20190115205839957-0115_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190115213243\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190115205839957-0115_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190115213243&h=67e79063&s={SIZE}\" />無綫節目《東張西望》索女主持利穎怡（Joan）嫁人喇！Joan擬結婚通知書曝光，將下嫁35歲關姓男友，她表示男友是她剛回流香港時認識，一齊經歷人生起伏，對於男友的地址顯示是青衣的屋邨，下嫁公屋男，Joan認為感情不應與金錢掛鈎：「佢陪我走過高高低低，家人都想我哋早啲結婚，但唔算閃婚，另一半係圈外人，我哋唔想太鋪張，想低調啲，大家都繼續以事業為重，多謝祝福。」另一位《東》主持朱智賢送上祝福：「好突然！好戥佢開心，好多人話《東張》好旺結婚生仔，好快又多個人妻喇！」"},{"pid":"39ac97ab343e21cb6a0dccf30cd26a72efd76a3d","tid":982931,"uid":94828,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"唔係拜金女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adfba6e8d1f6cb2cdfe691b774b46084163afdb","tid":982931,"uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ac97ab343e21cb6a0dccf30cd26a72efd76a3d","tid":982931,"uid":94828,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"唔係拜金女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"不嬲佢都唔係 一睇就知"},{"pid":"766e207bbed1c9d64eacc9604cf5b5e6d32ccaf6","tid